<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yīn zhe yé sū wǒ men yòu zài yī qǐ 迦南891</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yīn zhe yé sū wǒ men yòu zài yī qǐ, yīn zhe yé sū wǒ men yòu zài yī qǐ.
 yīn zhe yé sū wǒ men yòu zài yī qǐ, bǐ cǐ gǔ lì.
 jì dé cóng méng zhào de nà yī tiān qǐ, wǒ men dōu méi yǒu yóu yù.
 cóng cǐ wǒ men jiù lí kāi jiā, dào nà mò shēng de tǔ de.
 cóng cǐ shèng líng dài zhe wǒ men zǒu, cóng cǐ wǒ men jiù zài yī qǐ.
 yī tóng zūn shǒu zhǔ de zhǐ yì, yuàn yì xiàn shàng zì jǐ.
 jīn tiān wǒ men yòu yī tóng chàng, zhǔ a wǒ men yuàn yì xiàn shàng zì jǐ.
 wǒ men yuàn yì, wǒ men yuàn yì, wǒ men zhēn de yuàn yì.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>891</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>